Package: vmrestore
Version: __VERSION__
Architecture: all
Maintainer: James Doutsis <james@doutsis.com>
Depends: bash (>= 5.0), libvirt-daemon-system, qemu-utils, coreutils
Recommends: virtnbdbackup (>= 2.28)
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Description: Automated VM restoration tool for libvirt/KVM virtual machines
 Wraps virtnbdrestore to provide orchestrated VM restoration from vmbackup
 backup sets. Supports full, incremental, and copy backup types with
 point-in-time recovery, new-identity cloning, TPM/NVRAM state restoration,
 pre-flight space and disk safety checks, and archived chain recovery.
